headline: Axiad Names Accenture Customer of the Year
summary: Axiad, a global identity security leader, today announced that it has named Accenture its Customer of the Year for 2025. The recognition honors Accenture's visionary approach to securing its global enterprise through identity-first principles and celebrates the strategic collaboration in advancing the next generation of identity risk management.
